title: 06/27: Conner Discussion and Our First Ever Call-In Show! (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
James Conner may represent the first tough decision in Round 1 for Fantasy owners. We discuss his value at the top of the show and why he may end up being a second round pick when it's all said and done ... We're taking your phone calls via Skype today! Some topics covered include bonus scoring (9:15), Dak Prescott vs. Carson Wentz (18:00), late-round QBs to pair up (23:45) and some Dynasty questions ... What is Duke Johnson's dynasty value (40:00)? Should we expect a trade? And can you wait on TE in a 14-team league (43:30)? ... Your emails at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com.
Today's show is sponsored by NoBull. Visit NoBullProject.com\FFT
